Requirements:

    zlib

To install, run:
   
    LDFLAGS="-L$(psp-config --pspsdk-path)/lib" LIBS="-lc -lpspuser -lpspnet_inet -lpspnet_resolver -lpspnet" ./configure --host psp --prefix=$(psp-config --psp-prefix)
    make
    make install

See the "screenshot" directory for an example how to make a screenshot and how
to load a PNG image to screen.
